# Build artifacts.
#
# The repository previously carried Danantara_AIOS_Claude_Skills_v1.0_Draft.zip:
# a 642 KB snapshot of this same tree, committed inside the tree it snapshots.
# A distributable is built from a tagged commit, never committed alongside it.
# Attach release archives to a GitHub Release instead.
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Actual Condition Input Workbook, and any filled intake instrument.
#
# The workbook's own 99_LOOKUPS classification list offers Confidential,
# Market-Sensitive, and Sovereign-Sensitive. A filled workbook may carry all
# three. This repository has no classification boundary, so it is not a lawful
# home for that content — ingest it from outside via
# 06-scripts/ingest_actual_condition.py, which refuses a workbook found inside
# the repo.
*.xlsx
*.xlsm

# Derived from the workbook. Regenerate with ingest_actual_condition.py rather
# than committing a snapshot that silently goes stale against the source.
08-sources/tier2_index.json

# Local scratch
scratch/
tmp/
*.local.md
